t-dark-wolf-prime-video-recurring-guest-star-1235902798%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20play%20Chiefs'%20mascot%20KC%20Wolf%2C%20and%20this%20is%20why%20I'll%20be%20wearing%20SpongeBob%20SquarePants%20boxers%20at%20the%20Super%20Bowl%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dan%20Meers%20holds%20the%20head%20of%20his%20KC%20Wolf%20costume%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c5227043bb77284ba504c6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222919%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDan%20Meers%20has%20played%20KC%20Wolf%20for%2034%20years.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20Chiefs.com%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDan%20Meers%20has%20been%20the%20Kansas%20City%20Chiefs'%20mascot%2C%20KC%20Wolf%2C%20for%2034%20years.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EDespite%20a%20serious%20accident%2C%20Meers%20continued%20his%20mascot%20career%20after%20writing%20a%20book%20during%20recovery.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFor%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcategory%2Fsuper-bowl%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESuper%20Bowl%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20plans%20to%20wear%20a%20lucky%20pair%20of%20SpongeBob%20SquarePants%20boxer%20shorts.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20Dan%20Meers%2C%2057%2C%20who%20has%20played%20KC%20Wolf%2C%20the%20mascot%20for%20the%20Kansas%20City%20Chiefs%2C%20for%2034%20years.%20The%20conversation%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20grew%20up%20in%20St.%20Charles%2C%20Missouri%2C%20just%20outside%20St.%20Louis.%20I%20was%20always%20involved%20with%20sports.%20We%20were%20a%20family%20of%20three%20boys%2C%20and%20we%20played%20baseball%2C%20basketball%2C%20and%20football.%20Well%2C%20I%20should%20say%20my%20brother%20played.%20I%20was%20more%20of%20a%20benchwarmer.%20I%20went%20to%20the%20University%20of%20Missouri%2C%20and%20I%20knew%20I%20wasn't%20good%20enough%20to%20play%20at%20the%20Division%20One%20level.%20One%20day%20I%20was%20reading%20the%20school%20newspaper%2C%20and%20I%20saw%20that%20they%20were%20going%20to%20have%20tryouts%20to%20be%20Truman%20the%20Tiger%2C%20the%20school%20mascot.%20I%20got%20the%20job%2C%20and%20for%20the%20next%20four%20years%2C%20I%20ran%20around%20in%20a%20tiger%20suit%20at%20Mizzou.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20graduated%20college%2C%20I%20had%20this%20mascot%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%2C%20and%20I%20had%20a%20human%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9.%20I%20somehow%20get%20my%20first%20job%20working%20for%20the%20St.%20Louis%20Cardinals%2C%20playing%20their%20mascot%2C%20Fredbird.%20Then%20I%20get%20a%20call%20from%20the%20Kansas%20City%20Chiefs.%20They%20were%20starting%20up%20a%20new%20mascot%20program%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0this%20new%20KC%20Wolf%20character%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20wanted%20to%20know%20if%20I%20was%20interested.%20I'm%20like%2C%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnfl-tv-ratings-playoffs-super-bowl-streaming-broadcast-americans-culture-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efootball%3C%2Fa%3E%20they%20play%2010%20home%20games%20in%20the%20fall%20and%20the%20winter.%20And%20in%20baseball%2C%20they%20play%2081%20games%20in%20the%20summer.%20I'm%20not%20the%20brightest%20guy%20in%20the%20world%2C%20but%20I%20knew%20that%20sounded%20like%20a%20pretty%20good%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20I%20interviewed%20with%20the%20Chiefs%2C%20and%20I%20fell%20in%20love%20with%20them.%20I%20never%20dreamed%20that%20it%20would%20turn%20into%20a%20career.%20I%20originally%20thought%20I'd%20do%20it%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years%2C%20then%20get%20a%20real%20job%20like%20everybody%20else.%20Thirty-four%20years%20later%2C%20I'm%20sitting%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuper-bowl-lviii-economic-impact-hotel-prices-boulder-city-nevada-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVegas%20hotel%20room%3C%2Fa%3E%20getting%20ready%20to%20do%20my%20fourth%20Super%20Bowl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22KC%20Wolf%2C%20the%20Chiefs'%20mascot%2C%20on%20a%20four-wheeler%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c523916fcb546d2d4d98db%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EDan%20Meers%20has%20to%20be%20careful%20he%20doesn't%20drive%20the%20four-wheeler%20too%20fast.%3Cp%3EReed%20Hoffmann%2FAssociated%20Press%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EIt%20feels%20like%20I%20know%20half%20the%20population%20of%20Kansas%20City%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20fun%20job%2C%20don't%20get%20me%20wrong.%20I%20love%20what%20I%20do.%20But%20I%20don't%20just%20throw%20on%20a%20costume%20on%20a%20Sunday%20morning%2C%20do%20the%20game%2C%20and%20then%20wait%20until%20the%20next%20one%20rolls%20around.%20We%20do%20appearances%20all%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20walked%20five%20women%20down%20the%20aisle%20dressed%20as%20KC%20Wolf.%20I%20said%2C%20if%20I'm%20going%20to%20do%20this%2C%20I%20need%20to%20get%20a%20tuxedo%20so%20I%20can%20at%20least%20look%20good.%20So%20I%20went%20to%20my%20seamstress.%20She's%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20I%20think%20I%20could%20do%20that.%26quot%3B%20Now%20I've%20actually%20got%20a%20tuxedo%20that%20fits%20KC%20Wolf.%20I've%20been%20the%20best%20man%20in%20like%2010%20or%2011%20weddings.%20I%20didn't%20even%20know%20who%20the%20groom%20was.%20I%20stood%20in%20a%20wolf%20suit%2C%20wearing%20a%20tuxedo%2C%20holding%20a%20ring%20in%20my%20paw.%20Last%20year%2C%20I%20got%20to%20be%20a%20flower%20girl.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuper-bowl-lvii-media-day-eagles-chiefs-2023-2%23super-bowl-week-officially-kicked-off-on-monday-in-phoenix-arizona-with-a-huge-media-day-at-the-footprint-center-where-the-phoenix-suns-play-their-home-games-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EI%20do%20appearances%20constantly%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20can%20be%20at%20hospitals%2C%20community%20events%2C%20banks%2C%20grocery%20stores%2C%20parades%2C%20and%20festivals%20of%20all%20types.%20It's%20always%20a%20variety.%20That's%20what%20keeps%20the%20job%20interesting.%20The%20best%20part%20is%20the%20relationship%20you%20build%20with%20so%20many%20people.%20When%20I%20moved%20to%20Kansas%20City%2C%20I%20think%20I%20knew%20two%20people%20that%20I%20went%20to%20college%20with.%20At%20this%20point%2C%20I%20feel%20like%20I%20know%20about%20half%20the%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20week%2C%20ahead%20of%20the%20Super%20Bowl%2C%20we've%20got%2042%20KC%20Wolf%20appearances%20in%20Kansas%20City.%20And%20here%20in%20Vegas%2C%20I%20would%20say%20we%20will%20do%2015%20to%2018%20plus%20the%20game.%20It's%20just%20crazy%20busy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20did%20KC%20Wolf%20by%20myself%20for%20about%2015%20years%2C%20but%20it%20just%20got%20to%20a%20point%20where%20it%20was%20so%20busy%20that%20I%20said%20I'd%20have%20to%20have%20some%20more%20flexibility%20because%20I%20love%20being%20a%20mascot%2C%20but%20what%20I%20love%20more%20than%20that%20is%20my%20wife%20and%20my%20kids.%20I%20told%20the%20team%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20this%20job%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20going%20to%20sacrifice%20my%20family%20while%20I'm%20out%20entertaining%20other%20people's%20kids.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI've%20got%20several%20guys%20who%20help%20me%20now.%20They've%20all%20got%20their%20own%20costumes.%20But%20I'm%20still%20in%20charge%20of%20a%20wolf%20pack.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20stunt%20that%20nearly%20killed%20me%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20do%20a%20lot%20of%20speaking.%20A%20little%20over%2010%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20just%20about%20lost%20my%20life%20doing%20a%20stunt%20at%20the%20stadium.%20I%20fell%20about%2070%20feet.%20I%20was%20only%20supposed%20to%20drop%20about%2020%20feet.%20I%20broke%20seven%20ribs%2C%20had%20a%20collapsed%20lung%2C%20shattered%20my%20tailbone%2C%20cracked%20my%20sacrum%2C%20and%20got%20a%20big%20gash%20in%20the%20back%20of%20my%20left%20leg%20that%20required%20a%20lot%20of%20stitches.%20My%20worst%20injury%20was%20I%20broke%20the%20T12%20vertebrae.%20The%20first%20Chiefs%20game%20I%20missed%20in%2024%20years%20was%20because%20I%20was%20getting%20titanium%20rods%20installed%20in%20my%20back%20to%20stabilize%20my%20spine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20spent%20nine%20days%20in%20the%20hospital%20and%20six%20months%20off%20work%20doing%20therapy%20and%20rehab.%20The%20first%20couple%20of%20weeks%20I%20wondered%20what%20I%20would%20even%20be%20able%20to%20go%20back%20and%20do.%20But%20I%20was%20on%20year%2024.%20I'm%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BWho%20wants%20to%20stop%20at%2024%20when%20you've%20got%20your%2025th%20anniversary%20right%20in%20front%20of%20you%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20very%20grateful%20to%20work%20for%20an%20organization%20like%20the%20Chiefs%20that%20supports%20its%20employees.%20During%20those%20months%20off%20work%2C%20I%20knew%20I%20could%20sit%20around%20and%20feel%20sorry%20for%20myself%2C%20deal%20with%20all%20this%20pain%2C%20or%20I%20could%20do%20something%20productive%20with%20my%20time.%20So%20I%20wrote%20a%20book.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20funny%20thing%20about%20writing%20a%20book%20is%20people%20think%20you're%20smarter%20than%20you%20really%20are.%20Then%20I%20started%20doing%20corporate%20speaking%20and%20learned%20that%20if%20you're%20not%20boring%2C%20you%20can%20make%20people%20laugh%2C%20and%20you've%20got%20a%20good%20message%20to%20share%20that%20you%20get%20invited%20to%20other%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EMy%20SpongeBob%20SquarePants%20boxer%20shorts%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wouldn't%20consider%20myself%20a%20superstitious%20guy.%20But%20I%20do%20have%20one%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0I%20don't%20know%20if%20it's%20superstition%20or%20not%2C%20but%20I%20wear%20a%20pair%20of%20SpongeBob%20SquarePants%20boxer%20shorts%20under%20my%20wolf%20suit%20every%20game.%20That's%20probably%20more%20than%20people%20want%20to%20know%20about%20KC%20Wolf.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wore%20Homer%20Simpson%20boxer%20shorts%20for%20years%2C%20but%20we'd%20get%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20playoffs%2C%20and%20then%20we'd%20end%20up%20losing.%20And%20I'm%20like%2C%20%26quot%3BForget%20you%2C%20Homer%20Simpson.%20I'm%20done%20with%20you.%26quot%3B%20So%20I%20got%20rid%20of%20those%20and%20got%20myself%20a%20pair%20of%20SpongeBob%20Squarepants%2C%20and%20the%20next%20year%2C%20we%20won%20the%20Super%20Bowl.%20And%20I've%20been%20wearing%20them%20ever%20since.%20I'll%20have%20them%20on%20again%20this%20Sunday%20at%20the%20game.%20They%20don't%20exactly%20look%20good%2C%20but%20they%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20once%20heard%20that%20if%20you%20ask%20a%20man%20his%20occupation%2C%20you%20find%20out%20how%20he%20pays%20his%20bills.%20But%20if%20you%20ask%20a%20man%20his%20preoccupation%2C%20you%20discover%20his%20life's%20passion.%20I%20pay%20my%20bills%20running%20around%20in%20a%20costume%2C%20acting%20like%20a%20nut.%20What%20I'm%20truly%20passionate%20about%20is%20three%20things%3A%20Number%20one%20is%20my%20faith.%20Number%20two%2C%20my%20family.%20And%20number%20three%20is%20just%20using%20my%20life%20to%20make%20a%20positive%20impact%20in%20this%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20feel%20like%20my%20occupation%20and%20my%20calling%20are%20kind%20of%20the%20same.%20I%20get%20paid%20to%20go%20out%20and%20hopefully%20make%20a%20positive%20impact%20in%20this%20world%20by%20bringing%20laughter%20and%20smiles%20to%20others.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuper-bowl-kansas-city-chiefs-mascot-kc-wolf-dan-meers-2024-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707432381000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65c523ad917a1dae02449694%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuper-bowl-kansas-city-chiefs-mascot-kc-wolf-dan-meers-2024-2%22%2C%