halyzers%20for%20the%20general%20public%2C%20many%20of%20them%20have%20significant%20differences.%20Before%20purchasing%20one%20of%20the%20best%20breathalyzers%2C%20it's%20important%20to%20consider%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPrice%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20The%20cheapest%20product%20I%20tested%20was%20roughly%20%2440%2C%20while%20the%20most%20expensive%20was%20%24131.%20Generally%2C%20the%20more%20expensive%20breathalyzers%20tended%20to%20be%20more%20accurate%2C%20but%20you%20don't%20need%20the%20same%20level%20of%20detail%20for%20personal%20use%20as%20a%20police%20officer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAccuracy%20and%20reliability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Almost%20all%20major%20breathalyzer%20makers%20claim%20their%20products%20are%20either%20%26quot%3Bprofessional%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3Bpolice-grade%26quot%3B%20in%20terms%20of%20accuracy.%20This%20can%20make%20it%20hard%20to%20determine%20which%20deliver%20on%20that%20claim.%20Since%20accuracy%20is%20vital%2C%20I%20conducted%20different%20tests%20around%20the%20accuracy%20of%20each%20device%20to%20tell%20you%20which%20ones%20live%20up%20to%20their%20price%20tag.%20Ultimately%2C%20I%20discovered%20that%20price%20does%20not%20indicate%20reliability.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EResult%20readability%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Some%20breathalyzers%20can%20display%20a%20BAC%20reading%20directly%20on%20the%20device%2C%20while%20others%20rely%20on%20an%20optional%20or%20mandatory%20Bluetooth%20connection%20with%20a%20smartphone.%20Using%20a%20smartphone%20can%20be%20helpful%20if%20you%20intend%20to%20store%20results%20in%20a%20custom%20database.%20If%20you%20don't%20have%20or%20don't%20want%20to%20use%20a%20smartphone%2C%20a%20standalone%20device%20is%20your%20best%20option.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ECalibration%20and%20charging%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Many%20breathalyzers%20need%20to%20be%20recalibrated%20after%206-12%20months%20for%20the%20device%20to%20continue%20to%20accurately%20read%20BAC%20levels%20%E2%80%94%20and%20this%20has%2