rmat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EKevin%20Dietsch%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EBiden%20kept%20classified%20information%20hoping%20history%20would%20prove%20Obama%20wrong%2C%20according%20to%20Robert%20Hur.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBiden%20took%20particular%20exception%20to%20Obama's%20controversial%20decision%20to%20surge%20US%20troops%20in%20Afghanistan.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBiden's%20lawyers%20took%20exception%20to%20the%20notion%20that%20the%20now-president%20cared%20so%20much%20about%20the%20documents%20historical%20value.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESpecial%20Counsel%20Robert%20Hur%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspecial-counsel-on-biden-document-mishandling-doesnt-recommend-charges-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econcluded%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20kept%20classified%20information%20after%20leaving%20the%20vice%20presidency%20was%20to%20prove%20that%20President%20Barack%20Obama%20was%20wrong%20about%20surging%20US%20troops%20in%20Afghanistan%20in%202009.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDespite%20Mr.%20Biden's%20advice%2C%20President%20Obama%20ordered%20a%20surge%20of%20additional%20U.S.%20troops%2C%20and%20Mr.%20Biden's%20views%20endured%20sharp%20criticism%20from%20others%20within%20and%20outside%20of%20the%20administration.%20But%20he%20always%20believed%20history%20would%20prove%20him%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20Hur%20wrote%20in%20his%20nearly%20400-page%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20and%20Biden's%20personal%20lawyer%20took%20strong%20exception%20to%20elements%20of%20Hur's%20report.%20While%20not%20specifically%20mentioned%2C%20Hur%20repeatedly%20portrays%20the%20president%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiden-forgot-timing-vice-presidency-beau-death-special-counsel-report-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eas%20a%20confused%20old%20man%20with%20a%20declining%20memory%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERichard%20Stauber%2C%20special%20counsel%20to%20the%20president%2C%20and%20Bob%20Bauer%2C%20Biden's%20personal%20lawyer%2C%20took%20exception%20with%20how%20Hur%20described%20both%20the%20box%20that%20the%20Afghanistan%20memo%20was%20found%20in%20and%20the%20very%20notion%20that%20Biden%20was%20motivated%20by%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%5BT%5Dhe%202009%20Afghanistan%20policy%20review%20was%20one%20of%20the%20most%20widely%20covered%20foreign%20policy%20decisions%20in%20history.%20documented%20in%20near%20real-time%20by%20public%20releases%20of%20government%20documents%2C%20leaks%20to%20newspapers.%20and%20publications%20by%20writers%20like%20Bob%20Woodward.%20The%20idea%20that%20the%20President%20needed%20to%20keep%20any%20classified%20documents%20related%20to%20these%20events%2C%20let%20alone%20the%20particular%20ones%20found%20in%20his%20garage%2C%20is%20implausible%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20pair%20wrote%20to%20Hur%20after%20reviewing%20his%20report%20before%20its%20public%20release.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20Biden's%20lawyers%20allude%20to%2C%20Obama%20faced%20intense%20scrutiny%20over%20how%20the%20then-young%20president%20would%20handle%20the%20war%20in%20Afghanistan.%20Ultimately%2C%20President%20Obama%20sent%2030%2C000%20more%20troops%20that%20left%20the%20country%20by%202012.%20Biden%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20end%20what%20became%20America's%20longest%20war%20in%20August%202021%2C%20a%20chaotic%20ending%20that%20sent%20his%20approval%20ratings%20spiraling.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Hur%2C%20Biden%20kept%20%26quot%3Ba%20classified%20handwritten%20memo%20he%20sent%20President%20Obama%20over%20the%202009%20Thanksgiving%20holiday%2C%20and%20related%20marked%20classified%20documents.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20some%20damning%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspecial-counsel-report-biden-age-poor-memory-reason-no-charges-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eemb