panies%2Fresults%2Fads-take-blinkit-past-zomato-s-food-delivery-business-growth-in-q3-124020801835_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fresults%2Fads-take-blinkit-past-zomato-s-food-delivery-business-growth-in-q3-124020801835_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Military%20Personnel%20in%20Maldives%20Will%20Be%20Replaced%20With%20'Competent%20Indian%20Technical%20Personnel'%3A%20India%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F03232814%2FMuizzu-and-Modi.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20For%20the%20first%20time%2C%20India%20has%20announced%20that%20military%20personnel%20currently%20operating%20aviation%20platforms%20in%20the%20Maldives%20will%20be%20substituted%20with%20%E2%80%9Ccompetent%20Indian%20technical%20personnel.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20last%20week%E2%80%99s%20meeting%20of%20the%20core%20group%2C%20the%20Maldivian%20foreign%20ministry%20stated%20that%20India%20had%20agreed%20to%20%E2%80%9Creplace%E2%80%9D%20the%20military%20personnel%20in%20one%20of%20the%20three%20aircraft%20by%20March%2010%20and%20would%20complete%20%E2%80%9Creplacing%E2%80%9D%20the%20personnel%20in%20the%20other%20two%20by%20May%2010.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mea.gov.in%2Fpress-releases.htm%3Fdtl%2F37511%2FFirst_meeting_of_the_IndiaMaldives_High_Level_Core_Group%5C%22%3EThe%20Indian%20external%20affair%E2%80%99s%20readout%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20however%2C%20did%20not%20give%20the%20details%20and%20merely%20said%20that%20both%20countries%20had%20%E2%80%9Cagreed%20on%20a%20set%20of%20mutually%20workable%20solutions%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Findian-coast-guard-boats-maldives-muizzu-opposition-parliament%5C%22%3EOn%20Monday%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Maldivian%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20declared%20that%20India%20had%20agreed%20to%20%E2%80%9Cwithdraw%E2%80%9D%20its%20military%20personnel.%20That%20marked%20the%20first%20instance%20where%20the%20Maldives%20explicitly%20said%20that%20Indian%20personnel%20would%20be%20%E2%80%9Cwithdrawn%2C%E2%80%9D%20departing%20from%20the%20previous%20use%20of%20the%20ambiguous%20term%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Findia-to-replace-military-personnel-operating-aircraft-helicopters-maldives%5C%22%3Ereplace%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20by%20the%20foreign%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20later%2C%20India%20finally%20acknowledged%20that%20military%20personnel%20will%20be%20withdrawn%2C%20albeit%20without%20explicitly%20using%20that%20term.%20%E2%80%9CI%20would%20like%20to%20say%20that%20the%20present%20personnel%20will%20be%20replaced%20by%20competent%20Indian%20technical%20personnel%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20MEA%20spokesperson%20Randhir%20Jaiswal%20at%20the%20weekly%20briefing%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20expertise%20for%20operating%20these%20platforms%20are%20usually%20found%20among%20ex-servicemen%20who%20had%20operated%20such%20flights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnnouncing%20the%20withdrawal%20in%20his%20inaugural%20speech%20at%20the%20opening%20of%20parliament%2C%20Muizzu%20noted%20that%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20had%20been%20one%20of%20the%20key%20reasons%20for%20his%20successful%20electoral%20victory%20in%20the%20presidential%20elections.%20This%20demand%20had%20been%20cornerstone%20of%20the%20ruling%20alliance%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98India%20Out%E2%80%99%20campaign%2C%20which%20began%20in%202020.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuizzu%20officially%20requested%20India%20to%20withdraw%20its%20troops.%20Approximately%2080%20Indian%20military%20personnel%20are%20stationed%20in%20the%20Maldives%20to%20operate%20two%20helicopters%20and%20a%20Dornier%20plane%20for%20medical%20evacuation%20and%20search%20and%20rescue%20missions.%20During%20his%20meeting%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20in%20Dubai%2C%20both%20leaders%20agreed%20to%20establish%20a%20committee%20of%20officials%20to%20address%20this%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20core%20group%E2%80%99s%20inaugural%20meeting%20last%20month%2C%20Muizzu%20set%20a%20March%2015%20ultimatum%2C%20signalling%20the%20Maldives%E2%80%99%20desire%20for%20prompt%20action%20from%20India%20on%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707413848000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F03232814%2FMuizzu-and-Modi.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmilitary-personnel-in-maldives-will-be-replaced-with-competent-indian-technical-personnel-india%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22On%20February%205%20(Monday)%2C%20Maldivian%20President%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%20declared%20that%20India%20had%20agreed%20to%20%26quot%3Bwithdraw%26quot%3B%20its%20military%20personnel.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fsouth-asia%2Fmilitary-personnel-in-maldives-will-be-replaced-with-competent-indian-technical-personnel-india%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uttarakhand%3A%20Four%20Injured%20in%20Haldwani%20Violence%20After%20Madrasa%20Demolition%3B%20Shoot-At-Sight%20Orders%20Issued%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08210112%2Fimage-1817.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20At%20least%20four%20people%20have%20been%20injured%20in%20police%20firing%20in%20Uttarakhand%E2%80%99s%20Haldwani%2C%20where%20a%20Madarsa%20was%20demolished%20by%20municipal%20authorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20around%203%3A30%20pm%20on%20February%208%20(Thursday)%2C%20authorities%20arrived%20with%20bulldozers%20to%20demolish%20%E2%80%98Malik%20ke%20Bagiche%E2%80%99%20ka%20Madarsa.%20People%20on%20the%20ground%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20they%20had%20neither%20been%20shown%20any%20order%20to%20demolish%20their%20sacred%20worship%20place%20nor%20were%20the%20authorities%20ready%20to%20listen%20to%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELocals%20said%20that%20the%20officials%20refused%20to%20show%20the%20documents%20of%20the%20demolition%20order%20for%20the%20Madarsa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20women%20were%20beaten%20with%20lathis%20by%20male%20police%20officers%2C%20and%20at%20least%20four%20men%20were%20injured%20by%20bullets%20in%20the%20area%2C%E2%80%9D%20an%20eyewitness%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20learnt%20that%20officials%20only%20allowed%20two%20people%20to%20retrieve%20religious%20books%20on%20an%20immediate%20basis%20before%20demolishing%20the%20Madarsa.%20Despite%20people%E2%80%99s%20attempts%20and%20requests%20for%20officials%20to%20show%20the%20demolition%20order%2C%20they%20proceeded%20with%20force%2C%20leading%20to%20the%20escalation%20of%20the%20situation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20eyewitness%20quoted%20above%20further%20said%20that%20a%20few%20police%20officers%20also%20got%20injured%20due%20to%20retaliation%20by%20some%20people%20from%20the%20area.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20what%20wrong%20had%20the%20women%20done%20to%20them%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20Madarsa%2C%20demolished%20by%20the%20Uttarakhand%20authority%2C%20is%20located%20in%20the%20railway%20colony%20area%20where%20more%20than%204%2C000%20families%20reside.%20The%20Centre%20wants%20the%20land%20for%20railway%20expansion%2C%20and%20the%20matter%20is%20already%20being%20heard%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20according%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshoot-at-sight-orders-after-violence-during-uttarakhand-madrasa-demolition-5020128%23%3A~%3Atext%3DMore%2520than%252050%2520policemen%2520were%2CVanbhulpura%2520threw%2520stones%2520at%2520them.%5C%22%3Eto%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Futtarakhand-vi