%9Croaches%E2%80%9D%2C%20calling%20for%20their%20%E2%80%9Cextermination%E2%80%9D.%20The%20intention%20of%20the%20racist%20channel%20appears%20to%20be%20the%20propagation%20of%20hate%20among%20common%20Israelis%20against%20Palestinians%2C%20in%20line%20with%20the%20propaganda%20of%20the%20far-right%20government%20in%20Tel%20Aviv.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20channel%20prided%20itself%20on%20sharing%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.haaretz.com%2Fisrael-news%2Fsecurity-aviation%2F2023-12-12%2Fty-article%2F.premium%2Fgraphic-videos-and-incitement-how-the-idf-is-misleading-israelis-on-telegram%2F0000018c-5ab5-df2f-adac-febd01c30000%5C%22%3Eexclusive%20content%20from%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20and%20published%20over%20700%20posts%2C%20images%20and%20videos%20of%20terrorists%C2%A0being%20killed%20and%20of%20destruction%20in%20the%20Strip%20until%20December%2012%2C%202023.%20It%20urged%20its%205%2C300%20followers%20(as%20on%20December%2012%2C%202023)%20to%20share%20the%20content%20so%20that%20%E2%80%9Ceveryone%20can%20see%20that%20we%E2%80%99re%20screwing%20them%20(Palestinians).%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESample%20some%20of%20these%20posts%20from%20the%20channel%3A%20Every%20day%2C%20the%20channel%20posted%20graphic%20content%2C%20such%20as%20images%20of%20the%20dead%20bodies%20of%20Hamas%20terrorists%2C%20captioned%20%E2%80%9CShatter%20the%20terrorists%E2%80%99%20fantasy%E2%80%9D.%20Another%20post%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CBurning%20their%20mother%E2%80%A6%20You%20won%E2%80%99t%20believe%20the%20video%20we%20got!%20You%20can%20hear%20their%20bones%20crunch.%20We%E2%80%99ll%20post%20it%20right%20away%2C%20get%20ready.%E2%80%9D%20There%20was%20another%20post%20that%20was%20captioned%2C%20%E2%80%9CExterminating%20the%20roaches%E2%80%A6%20exterminating%20the%20Hamas%20rats%E2%80%A6%20Share%20this%20beauty.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2014%2C%20the%20channel%20posted%20a%20video%20with%20the%20caption%2C%20%E2%80%9CExclusive%20video%20of%