0launched%2520a%2520long%2520movement.%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20On%20December%2018%2C%202023%2C%20farmers%20sat%20on%20strike%20in%20front%20of%20the%20NTPC%20office%20located%20in%20Noida%20Sector-24.%20After%20the%20police%20stopped%20the%20protesters%20some%20distance%20before%20the%20main%20gate%20of%20NTPC%2C%20they%20staged%20a%20day%20and%20night%20strike%20there.%20These%20farmers%20of%2024%20villages%20say%20that%20they%20are%20affected%20by%20NTPC%E2%80%99s%20Dadri%20plant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20protest%20is%20being%20led%20by%20Bharatiya%20Kisan%20Parishad%20leader%20Sukhbir%20Khalifa.%20He%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9CFarmers%20protested%20at%20NTPC%20Dadri%20for%20several%20months%20and%20also%20launched%20a%20long%20movement.%20During%20this%2C%20several%20rounds%20of%20talks%20were%20held%20with%20the%20administration%20in%20which%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20farmers%20were%20considered%20justified%20but%20till%20now%20those%20demands%20have%20not%20been%20met.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20have%20come%20this%20time%20to%20fight%20a%20decisive%20battle.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ENewsclick%3C%2Fem%3E%20also%20reported%20on%20NTPC%E2%80%99s%20press%20release%20issued%20in%20December%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9Cto%20meet%20the%20need%20of%20electricity%20in%20the%20national%20interest%20including%20NCR%2C%20the%20construction%20of%20Stage-1%20of%20National%20Capital%20Power%20Station%20(NCPS)%20in%20Dadri%20region%20has%20been%20going%20on%20since%201986.%201995.%20The%20land%20acquisition%20and%20compensation%20were%20done%20as%20per%20the%20Land%20Acquisition%20Act%20existing%20at%20that%20time%20and%20the%20instructions%20of%20the%20district%20administration.%E2%80%9D%20NTPC%20also%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Cafter%20so%20many%20years%2C%20the%20protest%20is%20being%20held%20again%20with%20some%20demands.%20From%20time%20to%20time%2C%20during%20various%20talks%20with%20the%20protesters%2C%20NSPC%20has%20ma