0attention%20to%20what%20exceptional%20service%20of%20the%20highest%20order%20qualifies%20Advani%20for%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20revisiting%20his%20political%20legacy%20and%20contribution%20to%20Indian%20politics.%20This%20brings%20us%20to%20the%20time%20of%20aggressive%20Hindutva%20posturing%20through%20the%20Rath%20Yatra%20in%20the%2090s%2C%20whose%20architect-in-chief%20was%20Advani.%20Now%20retired%20from%20active%20political%20life%2C%20Advani%20is%20the%20early%20incarnation%20of%20aggressive%20right-wing%20Hindutva%20politics%20in%20the%20country%2C%20which%20fundamentally%20altered%20the%20language%20of%20Indian%20politics.%20He%20is%20the%20founding%20member%20of%20the%20BJP.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20unapologetic%20leader%20of%20militant%20Hindutva%20politics%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Andolan%20came%20as%20a%20watershed%20moment%20in%20Indian%20politics%20and%20made%20the%20ideology%20of%20Hindutva%20the%20political%20mainstream.%20The%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Yatra%20served%20multiple%20purposes%2C%20the%20most%20sacred%20being%20the%20political%20revival%20of%20right-wing%20Hindutva%20politics.%20It%20was%20during%20this%20time%20that%20Hindutva%20politics%20took%20a%20major%20militant%20turn.%20Lumpen%20organisations%20like%20Bajrang%20Dal%20and%20Vishwa%20Hindu%20Parishad%20became%20compulsory%20elements%20in%20composing%20communal%20violence%20and%20polarising%20the%20electorate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindu%20right%E2%80%99s%20search%20for%20a%20new%20lease%20of%20political%20life%20brought%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20movement%20to%20the%20epicentre%20of%20political%20mobilisation.%20Ram%20mandir%20andolan%20was%20also%20an%20upper-caste%20conservative%20revolution%20that%20brought%20the%20Hindu%20majority%E2%80%99s%20religious%20sentiments%20to%20the%20centre%20of%20political%20discourse%20to%20limit%20the%20impact%20of%20Mandal%20democratisation%20and%20create%20a%20political%20Hindu%20vote%20bank%20through%20the%20cooptation%20of%20non-dominant%20castes%20and%20organised%20enmity%20against%20minorities.%20The%20organised%20enmity%20against%20Muslims%20became%20the%20mass%20mobilisation%20plank%20of%20Hindutva%20politics%20since%20the%20time%20of%20Advani%2C%20whose%20most%20evocative%20display%20happened%20during%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20Yatra.%20Advani%20occasionally%20expressed%20his%20inherent%20disdain%20against%20the%20subaltern%20political%20assertion%20by%20accusing%20Mandal%20politics%20of%20dividing%20Hindus%2C%20which%20the%20Yatra%20undone%20through%20a%20spiritual%20unity%20amongst%20Hindus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fl-k-advani-from-rath-yatra-to-bharat-ratna%5C%22%3ELK%20Advani%3A%20From%20Rath%20Yatra%20to%20Bharat%20Ratna%2C%20a%20Political%20Journey%20Propelled%20By%20Violence%2C%20Polarisation%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20political%20spirituality%20of%20Rath%20Yatra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20procession%20of%20Rath%20Yatra%20was%20designed%20to%20create%20a%20political%20awakening%20of%20the%20Hindu%20nation%2C%20standing%20united%20with%20anger%20against%20the%20civilisational%20assault%20over%20religion%2C%20which%20continued%20even%20after%20independence%20through%20pseudo-secularism.%20As%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.co.in%2Fbooks%2Fabout%2FRoutine_Violence.html%3Fid%3Dca7qES8Z9hAC%26redir_esc%3Dy%5C%22%3EGyanendra%20Pandey%3C%2Fa%3E%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20conflict%20over%20the%20Babri%20Masjid%20in%20Ayodhya%20is%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20Hindu%20drive%20to%20reclaim%20the%20national%20culture%20from%20its%20enemies%20%E2%80%93Muslims%2C%20but%20also%20secularists%20and%20Westernisers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chariot-themed%20design%20of%20Toyota%20Van%20had%20the%20portrait%20of%20Advani%20with%20slogans%20making%20clarion%20calls%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%20movement.%20Writing%20about%20Babri%20Masjid%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fbooks.google.co.in%2Fbooks%2Fabout%2FMaking_India_Hindu.html%3Fid%3DnnJ1AAAAMAAJ%26redir_esc%3Dy%5C%22%3ERichard%20Davis%3C%2Fa%3E%20mentions%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20choice%20of%20site%20juxtaposes%20two%20figures%20well%20known%20to%20most%20people%20in%20north%20India%3A%20Ram%20and%20Babar.%20As%20God%20and%20human%2C%20they%20are%20made%20to%20stand%20for%20two%20religions%20%E2%80%93%20Hinduism%20and%20Islam%20%E2%80%93%20in%20a%20highly%20imbalanced%20manner%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20movement%20had%20a%20mass%20orientation%2C%20intended%20to%20create%20a%20communal%20commotion%20and%20carve%20a%20sacred%20nation%20space%2C%20with%20Ayodhya%20at%20its%20centre.%20%C2%A0This%20projected%C2%A0%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%20as%20a%20national%20issue%20whose%20liberation%20entailed%20undoing%20the%20historical%20wrongs%20inflicted%20by%20the%20Muslim%20others%20on%20the%20Hindu%20religion.%20The%2035-day%20Yatra%20of%20Advani%20had%20an%20approximate%2010%2C000%20km%20long%20route%2C%20covering%20eight%20North%20Indian%20states%20of%20Sangh%20stronghold%20in%20the%20Hindi%20heartland.%20It%20started%20from%20Somnath%20temple%2C%20having%20symbolic%20importance%20to%20the%20Hindutva%20assertion.%20For%20Advani%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20reconstruction%20of%20Somnath%20was%20the%20first%20chapter%20in%20a%20journey%20to%20pre%C2%ADserve%20the%20old%20symbols%20of%20unity%2C%20communal%20amity%2C%20and%20cultural%20oneness%20to%20be%20succeeded%20by%20the%20Ram%20Janmabhoomi%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F15133951%2Fmodi-advani.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Narendra%20Modi%20with%20L.K.%20Advani%20during%20Advani's%20rath%20yatra.%20Credit%3A%20Twitter%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22646%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F15133951%2Fmodi-advani.jpg%20454w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F15133951%2Fmodi-advani-300x272.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-205233%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22585%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ENarendra%20Modi%20with%20L.K.%20Advani%20during%20Advani%E2%80%99s%20rath%20yatra.%20Credit%3A%20Twitter%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20event%20witnessed%20the%20active%20participation%20of%20Sangh%E2%80%99s%20militant%20subsidiary%20organisations%20armed%20with%20weapons%2C%20bringing%20a%20militant%20Hindutva%20zeal%20to%20the%20yatra.%20The%20violent%20ceremonious%20processions%20were%20actively%20endorsed%20and%20supported%20by%20Advani.%20He%20was%20given%20a%20forehead%20tilak%20of%20blood%20in%20Ujjain%20by%20militants%20of%20VHP.%20Songs%2C%20slogans%20and%20speeches%20exhorted%20communal%20sentiments%20and%20demonised%20Muslims%2C%20inciting%20communal%20conflict%20throughout%20the%20itinerary.%20They%20were%20clearly%20designed%20to%20create%20Hindu%20militancy%20and%20raise%20the%20religious%20consciousness%20of%20Hindus%20on%20communal%20lines.%20The%20outcome%20was%20predictable.%20Town%20after%20town%20succumbed%20to%20riots%2C%20arson%2C%20killings%2C%20and%20curfew.%20The%20Yatra%20resulted%20in%20communal%20riots%20in%20most%20of%20the%20cities%2C%20spreading%20anti-muslim%20evocation%20of%20violent%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBacked%20by%20planned%20rumours%20and%20incendiary%20propaganda%2C%20the%20Yatra%20succeeded%20in%20creating%20a%20geography%20of%20violence%20and%20aggrandised%20communal%20polarisation.%20The%20riots%20shaped%20the%20social%20psyche%20of%20the%20Hindus%20to%20embrace%20the%20religious%20identity%20and%20rally%20behind%20the%20cause%20of%20Ram%20Mandir.%20The%20cynical%20exploitation%20of%20religious%20imagery%20for%20political%20ends%20made%20the%20BJP%20the%20natural%20party%20of%20Hindus.%20This%20yatra%2C%20engineered%20by%20Advani%2C%20brought%20fortunes%20to%20the%20BJP%20which%20witnessed%20an%20astounding%20political%20success%20in%20subsequent%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20principles%20of%20law%20and%20Rath%20Yatra%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20yatra%2C%20Advani%20showed%20an%20open%20disregard%20for%20the%20land%20of%20law%2C%20constitutional%20principles%20of%20secularism%20and%20adjudicatory%20powers%20of%20the%20Indian%20judiciary.%20He%20found%20the%20temple%20movement%20to%20be%20a%20matter%20of%20popular%20Hindu%20faith%20that%20could%20not%20be%20decided%20by%20science%2C%20history%2C%20or%20law.%20He%20questioned%20the%20secular%20principles%20of%20the%20constitution%20and%20demanded%20that%20the%20Hindu%20sovereignty%20over%20the%20sacred%20space%20be%20granted%20and%20that%20the%20judiciary%20should%20not%20adjudicate%20matters%20of%20faith.%20Time%20flattened%20these%20appeals%20of%20Advani%20as%20Ram%20Temple%20stands%20on%20the%20ruins%20of%20the%20Mosque%2C%20as%20decided%20by%20the%20judiciary%20and%20inaugurated%20by%20the%20Indian%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20anything%2C%20Advani%20curated%20the%20current%20brand%20of%20Hindutva%20politics.%20The%20culture%20of%20mob%20violence%20and%20Hindu%20majoritarian%20politics%20have%20trumped%20electoral%20politics.%20Hindutva%20has%20become%20the%20hegemonic%20political%20discourse%20and%20minorities%20are%20being%20relegated%20to%20a%20substandard%20location.%20Secular%20credentials%20of%20the%20constitutions%20are%20subverted%20by%20the%20Indian%20state.%20From%20dormant%20to%20a%20hegemonic%20political%20mainstream%2C%20the%20Hindutva%20politics%20of%20BJP%20grew%20in%20the%20shadow%20of%20leaders%20like%20Advani.%20His%20acquittance%20in%20the%20Babri%20demolition%20and%20subsequent%20awarding%20of%20Bharat%20Ratna%20narrates%20the%20tale%20of%20communal%20evolution%20in%20Indian%20politics%20and%20its%20grand%20success.%20The%20hero%20of%20Hindutva%20politics%20receives%20the%20official%20recognition%20of%20Bharat%20Ratna.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHimanshu%20Shukla%20is%20a%20PhD%20scholar%20at%20the%20Centre%20for%20Political%20Studies%2C%20JNU.%20Shukla%20tweets%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F135Himanshu%5C%22%3E%40135Himanshu%3C%2Fa%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707380437000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08123957%2FEffect-2024-02-08T123938.496.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbharat-ratna-to-lk-advani-signals-the-grand-success-of-communal-politics%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Rath%20Yatra%2C%20engineered%20by%20Advani%2C%20brought%20fortunes%20to%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20which%20witnessed%20an%20astounding%20political%20success%20in%20subsequent%20elections.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbharat-ratna-to-lk-advani-signals-the-grand-success-of-communal-politics%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Congress%20Releases%20%E2%80%98Black%20Paper%E2%80%99%20on%20Modi%20Government%E2%80%99s%20Failures%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08133122%2FModi-Kharge.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20Congress%20on%20Thursday%20(February%208)%20released%20a%20black%20paper%20on%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20failures%2C%20highlighting%20economic%2C%20social%20and%20political%20injustices%20in%20the%20last%20ten%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2054-page%20document%2C%20titled%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3E10%20Saal%20Anyay%20Kal%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%2C%20released%20by%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20in%20the%20national%20capital%2C%20claims%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20in%20its%20ten%20years%20in%20power%20has%20%E2%80%9Cdevastated%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20economy%2C%20aggravated%20unemployment%2C%20destroyed%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20agricultural%20sector%2C%20abetted%20crimes%20against%20women%20and%20committed%20grave%20injustices%20against%20minorities%20in%20the%20country%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CToday%20we%20are%20bringing%20out%20a%20%E2%80%98Black%20Paper%E2%80%99%20against%20the%20government.%20Whenever%20PM%20Modi%20presents%20his%20views%20in%20Parliament%2C%20he%20hides%20his%20failures.%20At%20the%20same%20time%2C%20when%20we%20speak%20about%20the%20failures%20of%20the%20government%2C%20it%20is%20not%20given%20importance.%20Therefore%2C%20we%20want%20to%20bring%20out%20a%20Black%20Paper%20and%20tell%20the%20public%20about%20the%20failures%20of%20the%20government%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Kharge.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20move%20to%20release%20the%20%E2%80%9Cblack%20paper%E2%80%9D%20comes%20amid%20speculation%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20will%20bring%20a%20white%20paper%20in%20parliament%20to%20highlight%20the%20economic%20failures%20of%20the%20UPA%20between%202004%20and%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20BJP%20MP%20Jayant%20Sinha%2C%20who%20is%20also%20the%20member%20of%20the%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Finance%2C%20said%20that%20a%20white%20paper%20will%20be%20brought%20to%20the%20house.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndia%E2%80%99s%20GDP%20growth%20had%20slowed%20down%20to%205%25%2C%20inflation%20had%20risen%20to%2010%25%2C%20The%20country%20was%20facing%20a%20balance%20of%20payment%20crisis.%20The%20baking%20system%20was%20in%20a%20crisis.%20Everyone%20was%20leaving%20the%20country%20and%20we%20were%20in%20the%20fragile%20economies%20in%20the%20world.%20This%20is%20the%20condition%20in%20which%20the%20UPA%20had%20left%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%20in%20his%20remarks%20on%20the%20interim%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20white%20paper%2C%20we%20will%20clarify%20what%20was%20the%20position%20of%20the%20economy%20(before%202014)%20%E2%80%A6%20and%20how%20we%20have%20tackled%20the%20economic%20problems.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ongoing%20interim%20budget%20session%20of%20parliament%20which%20was%20slated%20to%20end%20on%20Friday%20has%20also%20been%20extended%20by%20a%20day%20to%20Saturday%2C%20when%20the%20white%20paper%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20presented.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20Black%20Paper%20claims%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20%E2%80%9Cblack%20paper%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Congress%20has%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20years%20have%20been%20%E2%80%9Cmarked%20by%20high%20rates%20of%20unemployment%2C%20economic%20catastrophes%20such%20as%20demonetisation%20and%20flawed%20GST%2C%20which%20have%20only%20increased%20the%20divide%20between%20the%20rich%20and%20the%20poor%20and%20devastated%20the%20future%20of%20millions%20of%20farmers%20and%20daily%20wage%20workers%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20highlighted%20the%20highest%20unemployment%20rate%20in%2045%20years%2C%20prices%20of%20essential%20commodities%20being%20at%20an%20all-time%20high%2C%20and%20failure%20to%20increase%20MSP%20for%20farmers%20despite%20a%20promise%20to%20double%20their%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETerming%20it%20%E2%80%9CModani%20Raj%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20party%20has%20also%20accused%20the%20Modi%20government%20of%20%E2%80%9Cneutering%E2%80%9D%20investigative%20agencies%20despite%20a%20promise%20to%20eliminate%20safe%20havens%C2%A0%20for%20economic%20offenders%20and%20facilitating%20crony%20capitalism.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20%3Cem%3Esamajik%20anyay%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20social%20injustice%2C%20the%20party%20has%20claimed%20that%20the%20last%20decade%20has%20seen%20%E2%80%9Cblatant%20discrimination%20and%20severe%20oppression%20against%20women%2C%20SC%2CSTs%2COBCs%20and%20minorities%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIts%20politics%20of%20hatred%2C%20polarisation%20and%20divide%20has%20destroyed%20the%20social%20fabric%20of%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20document%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20%3Cem%3Erajneetik%20anyay%3C%2Fem%3E%20(political%20injustice)%20the%20Congress%20has%20accused%20the%20Modi%20government%20of%20remaining%20silent%20on%20China%E2%80%99s%20encroachments%20on%20Indian%20territory%2C%20%E2%80%9Cundermining%20the%20Army%20with%20the%20Agneepath%20scheme%E2%80%9D%20and%20targeting%20opposition%20with%20its%20investigative%20agencies%20and%20%E2%80%9Cending%20the%20independence%20of%20the%20media%E2%80%9D%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Election%20Commission%2C%20ED%20and%20RBI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CModi%20government%20talks%20about%20Nehru%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKharge%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20never%20talks%20about%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbiggest%20issue%20in%20the%20country%20which%20is%20unemployment%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThey%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnarendra-modi-caste-nehru-rajya-sabha%5C%22%3E%20talk%20about%20Nehru%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20don%E2%80%99t%20talk%20about%20how%20many%20people%20were%20given%20jobs%20through%20public%20sector%20jobs.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20ongoing%20protests%20by%20non-BJP%20state%20governments%20in%20the%20national%20capital%20against%20%E2%80%9Ctax%20injustice%E2%80%9D%2C%20Kharge%20said%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20does%20not%20release%20funds%20to%20states%20and%20then%20accuses%20them%20of%20not%20spending%20the%20money%20released%20by%20the%20Centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETaking%20a%20jibe%20at%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20assertion%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20he%20had%20given%20rights%20to%20SC%2FST%2FOBCs%2C%20Kharge%20said%20that%20the%20UPA%20government%20had%20also%20given%20them%20rights%20but%20does%20not%20want%20to%20list%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20these%20are%20emotional%20issues.%20But%20giving%20employment%20is%20important.%20He%20should%20talk%20about%20it.%20You%20can%20talk%20about%20social%20justice%20when%20everyone%20has%20a%20share%20in%20development.%20Why%20are%20we%20insisting%20on%20the%20public%20sector%3F%20When%20PSUs%20are%20formed%2C%20SC-ST%2C%20OBC%20and%20tribals%20get%20employment%20and%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20run%20around%20for%20daily%20wage%20jobs.%20It%20gives%20them%20stability.%20We%20want%20them%20to%20have%20steady%20jobs%20in%20government%20jobs%20and%20the%20public%20sector%20and%20if%20small%20scale%20industries%20have%20to%20be%20established%2C%20they%20should%20be%20hand%20held%20like%20they%20are%20given%20to%20big%20capitalists%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKharge%20added%20that%20the%20Congress%20had%20ensured%20India%E2%80%99s%20independence%20and%20in%202024%2C%20it%20will%20take%20the%20country%20out%20of%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%9Cdarkness%20of%20injustice%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EModi%E2%80%99s%20response%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20in%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20in%20his%20farewell%20speech%20for%20the%20retiring%20members%20of%20the%20House%2C%20Modi%20said%20that%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20black%20paper%20was%20like%20a%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ekaala%20teeka%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9D%20for%20his%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%20that%20Khargeji%20has%20come%20I%20have%20to%20fulfill%20my%20dharma%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20child%20gets%20ready%20for%20an%20occasion%20and%20wears%20nice%20clothes%2C%20we%20put%20a%20kaala%20tika%20to%20ward%20off%20evil%20eye.%20Today%20in%20the%20last%20ten%20years%20the%20country%20is%20stepping%20on%20new%20steps%20of%20development.%20That%20is%20why%20I%20thank%20Khargeji%20for%20giving%20this%20kaala%20teeka%20today%20for%20our%20government.%20I%20thought%20people%20will%20come%20in%20black%20clothes%20today%20but%20they%20have%20gone%20up%20to%20a%20black%20paper%20now.%20But%20I%20welcome%20that%20as%20well.%20Because%20whenever%20something%20good%20happens%2C%20kaala%20teeka%20is%20necessary.%20And%20if%20an%20aged%20person%20like%20Khargeji%20does%20it%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20even%20more%20welcome%20for%20us.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707379763000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F08133122%2FModi-Kharge.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-releases-black-paper-on-modi-governments-failures%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%2054-page%20document%20comes%20ahead%20of%20the%20buzz%20that%20the%20Modi%20government%20will%20put%20out%20a%20'White%20Paper'%20making%20comparisons%20with%20Manmohan%20Singh's%20tenure.%20The%20paper%20claims%20that%20ten%20years%20devastated%20the%20country's%20economy%2C%20aggravated%20unemployment%2C%20destroyed%20the%20country's%20agricultural%20sector%2C%20%26quot%3Babetted%20crimes%20against%20women%20and%20committed%20grave%20injustices%20against%20minorities%20in%20the%20country.%E2%80%9D%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A13%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcongress-releases-black-paper-on-modi-governments-failures%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20Supreme%20Court%20Heads%20Into%20Dangerous%20Territory%20as%20It%20Considers%20Trump%20Insurrection%26nbsp%3BCase%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F01%2F05123915%2FScreenshot-2024-01-05-at-12.38.4.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3ECan%20Colorado%20disqualify%20former%20President%20Trump%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.oyez.org%2Fcases%2F2023%2F23-719%5C%22%3Efrom%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20primary%20ballot%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20That%E2%80%99s%20the%20momentous%20question%20the%20U.S.%20Supreme%20Court%20will%20consider%20in