0officials%20from%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20(MHA)%20on%20February%207.%20The%20government%20team%20was%20led%20by%20A.K%20Mishra%2C%20Adviser%2C%20Northeast%2C%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%2C%20and%20Intelligence%20Bureau%20officials.%20Concerns%20over%20the%20scrapping%20of%20the%20Free%20Movement%20Regime%20with%20Myanmar%20were%20raised%20at%20the%20three-hour%20long%20meeting%20and%20the%20January%2024%20Kangla%20Fort%20incident%20in%20Imphal%20when%20Arambai%20Tenggol%2C%20a%20radical%20Meitei%20group%2C%20administered%20oath%20to%20elected%20representatives%20to%20supposedly%20%E2%80%98protect%20the%20integrity%20of%20Manipur%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20tribal%20delegation%20is%20also%20reported%20to%20have%20broached%20concerns%20over%20%E2%80%9Ccontinued%20power%20outages%20in%20the%20hill%20districts%20of%20Churachandpur%20and%20Pherzawl%2C%E2%80%9D%20where%20hill%20tribals%20mostly%20reside.%20The%20territorial%20divisions%20across%20the%20sensitive%20border%20state%20have%20acquired%20political%20dimensions%20after%20the%20state%20has%20been%20in%20a%20state%20of%20turmoil%20since%20May%203%2C%20with%20over%20200%20persons%20dead%2C%20around%20300%20churches%20vandalised%20or%20destroyed%20and%2067%2C000%20persons%20internally%20displaced.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20delegate%20who%20was%20a%20part%20of%20the%20meeting%20told%20the%20newspaper%20that%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20administration%20for%20the%20Kuki-Zo%20people%20is%20still%20on%20the%20table%20and%20%E2%80%9Cthey%20would%20continue%20to%20press%20for%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20meeting%20follows%20Manipur%20Chief%20Minister%20N.%20Biren%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20Delhi%20visit%20on%20February%203%2C%20when%20he%20met%20Amit%20Shah.%20On%20Tuesday%2C%20Shah%20announced%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20fence%20the%20entire%20