Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSmFi6RklPBY%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDainik%20Bhaskar%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3EAnimal%3C%2Fem%3E%20director%20targeted%20Kiran%20Rao%20apropos%20of%20an%20old%20comment%20in%20which%20she%20called%20out%20certain%20films%20for%20blurring%20the%20line%20between%20stalking%20and%20wooing.%20He%20told%20Dainik%20Bhaskar%20(translated%20from%20Hindi)%3A%20%26quot%3BToday%20morning%2C%20my%20AD%20showed%20me%20an%20article.%20It%20is%20of%20the%20second%20ex-wife%20of%20a%20superstar.%20She%20is%20saying%20that%20films%20like%20%3Cem%3EBahubaali%202%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3EKabir%20Singh%3C%2Fem%3E%20promote%20misogyny%20and%20stalking.%20I%20think%20she%20does%20not%20know%20the%20difference%20between%20stalking%20and%20approaching.%20When%20people%20read%20these%20things%20out%20of%20context%2C%20they%20tend%20to%20agree.%20This%20is%20entirely%20wrong.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWHAT%20KIRAN%20RAO%20SAID%20LAST%20YEAR%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20November%202023%2C%20Kiran%20Rao%20called%20for%20gender%20sensitisation%20at%20a%20session%20while%20citing%20a%20Tata%20Institute%20of%20Social%20Sciences%20report%20that%20included%20%26quot%3Bstalking%20as%20one%20of%20the%20most%20glorified%20forms%20of%20wooing%20a%20woman%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%93%20films%20such%20as%20these%20do%20very%20well%2C%20said%20Ms%20Rao%20naming%20Kabir%20Singh.%20%26quot%3BAnother%20very%20big%20film%2C%20which%20I%20find%20fascinating%2C%20was%20%3Cem%3EBaahubali%201%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3E(Baahubali%3A%20The%20Beginning%3C%2Fem%3E).%20It%20started%20off%20with%20this%20exciting%20fight%20sequence%2C%20where%20this%20woman%20is%20leaping%20from%20tree%20to%20tree%2C%20and%20she%20is%20a%20warrior.%20But%20the%20hero%20delicately%20strips%20her%20of%20her%20agency%20and%20makes%20her%20just%20a%20fantastic%20romantic%20interest.%20I%20find%20it%20fascinating.%20It%20is%20(one%20of)%20the%20biggest%20films%20of%20Indian%20cinema%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added%2C%20as%20reported%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fkiran-rao-movies-glorifying-stalking-as-wooing-tend-to-do-extremely-well%2Farticleshow%2F105138310.cms%3Ffrom%3Dmdr%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETimes%20Of%20India.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESANDEEP%20REDDY%20VANGA%20NAME%20CHECKS%20AAMIR%20KHAN%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndian%20mainstream%20cinema%20has%20long%20been%20accused%20of%20promoting%20stalking%20and%20rejecting%20the%20notion%20of%20consent.%20Mr%20Vanga%20compounded%20his%20dismissal%20of%20a%20very%20serious%20concern%20with%20whataboutery%2C%20referencing%20Kiran%20Rao's%20ex-husband%20Aamir%20Khan's%201990%20film%20%3Cem%3EDil%3C%2Fem%3E.%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3EMain%20kehna%20chahunga%20uss%20aurat%20ko%20ki%20jaake%3C%2Fem%3E%20Aamir%20Khan%20%3Cem%3Eko%20pucho%20'Khambe%20jaisi%20khadi%20hai%2C%20Ladki%20hai%20ya%20fuljari%20hai'%20woh%20kya%20tha%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20Then%20come%20back%20to%20me.%20That%20is%2C%20%3Cem%3Ematlab%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20if%20you%20remember%20Dil%2C%20almost%20rape%20attempt%20%3Cem%3Etak%20leke%20jaake%20usko%20ehsaas%20jatata%20hai%20ki%20isne%20galat%20kiya.%20Aur%20usko%20pyar%20ho%20jata%20hai.%20Yeh%20sab%20kya%20hai%3C%2Fem%3E%3F%20(I%20would%20like%20to%20say%20to%20that%20woman%2C%20'Go%20ask%20Aamir%20Khan%2C%20'Is%20she%20like%20a%20pillar%2C%20a%20girl%2C%20or%20a%20firecracker%3F'%20What%20was%20that%3F%26quot%3B%20Then%20come%20back%20to%20me.%20If%20you%20remember%20Dil%2C%20he%20almost%20creates%20the%20situation%20towards%20an%20attempted%20rape%2C%20and%20it%20makes%20her%20realise%20that%20she%20was%20wrong.%20She%20ultimately%20falls%20in%20love.%20What%20is%20all%20this%3F)%20I%20don't%20understand%20why%20they%20attack%20like%20that%20before%20checking%20the%20surroundings%2C%26quot%3B%20Sandeep%20Reddy%20Vanga%20told%20Dainik%20Bha