eaching%20and%20provide%20guidance%20on%20improvement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20hands-on%20approach%20not%20only%20equips%20teachers%20to%20impart%20knowledge%20effectively%20but%20also%20strives%20to%20establish%20a%20sustainable%20model.%20The%20goal%20is%20to%20empower%20teachers%20to%20continue%20delivering%20quality%20education%20independently%2C%20even%20without%20ongoing%20assistance%20from%20the%20NGO.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20idea%20is%20to%20improve%20children%E2%80%99s%20conceptual%20understanding%20of%20science.%20Based%20on%20our%20observation%2C%20many%20students%20lose%20interest%20in%20science%20in%20Classes%206%20to%209.%20Girl%20students%20too%20face%20several%20biases%20and%20challenges%20as%20STEM%20courses%20are%20not%20traditionally%20considered%20a%20woman%E2%80%99s%20domain.%20If%20they%20get%20a%20better%20understanding%20of%20scientific%20concepts%20through%20innovative%20methods%2C%20there%20is%20a%20possibility%20of%20them%20choosing%20a%20career%20in%20science%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Mabel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdapting%20to%20the%20specific%20needs%20and%20interests%20of%20each%20school%20management%2C%20L%26amp%3BT%20enhances%20the%20physical%20infrastructure%20based%20on%20demand.%20What%20started%20with%2065%20schools%20has%20now%20expanded%20to%20include%20208%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeachers%20share%20that%20the%20presence%20of%20these%20models%20not%20only%20allows%20students%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F340084%2Fgujarat-school-for-the-blind-and-visually-impaired-inclusive-design-architecture-by-anand-sonecha-sealabs%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshowcase%20their%20creativity%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20also%20aids%20teachers%20in%20delivering%20more%20effective%20explanations%2C%20utilising%20the%20visual%20aids%20provided%20by%20the%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20we%20would%20just%20explain%20concepts%2C%20with%20children%20not%20being%20able%20to%20see%20how%20it%20works.%20Through%20these%20models%20and%20kits%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20demonstrate%20how%20the%20concept%20works%2C%20helping%20in%20easier%20understanding.%20Children%20also%20ask%20more%20questions.%20The%20concept%20reaches%20them%20easily%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Veeramuthu%20N%2C%20a%20teacher%20from%20Government%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%2C%20Kaliannanpudur%2C%20Coimbatore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20L%26amp%3BT%20has%20provided%20them%20with%2075%20kits%2C%20which%20include%20working%20models%2C%20explanatory%20models%20and%20charts.%20Children%20are%20taken%20to%20the%20lab%2C%20where%20they%20can%20experiment.%20Alternatively%2C%20teachers%20also%20bring%20the%20models%20to%20class%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20concept%20they%20are%20teaching.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%2C%20NGO%20partners%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20the%20American%20India%20Foundation%20(AIF)%20and%20Don%20Bosco%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20%E2%80%94%20offer%20after-school%20classes%20for%20students.%20These%20sessions%20cover%20a%20range%20of%20topics%2C%20including%20mobile%20application%20development%2C%20coding%2C%20CNC%20machining%2C%20sensors%2C%20map%20making%2C%203D%20printing%2C%20and%20more.%20The%20knowledge%20gained%20in%20these%20classes%20empowers%20children%20to%20apply%20these%20concepts%20to%20solve%20real-life%20problems%20they%20encounter%20in%20their%20daily%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFiring%20the%20creativity%20in%20children%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2FIMG20240203121913-1-min-1707141250-scaled.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20winners%20made%20an%20agricultural%20tricyle%20using%20scrap%20materials%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F