20using%20different%20farming%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUsing%20IoT%2C%20we%20have%20made%20the%20robot%20remotely%20controllable.%20For%20instance%2C%20if%20you%20want%20to%20use%20the%20robot%20from%20Jaipur%20city%20and%20your%20crops%20are%20in%20Kota%2C%20you%20can%20simply%20log%20in%20to%20the%20application%20that%20I%20have%20developed%20and%20use%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-5-1706885027.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aryan%20won%20the%20Bal%20Shakti%20Award%20for%20his%20innovation.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-5-1706885027.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-5-1706885027-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-5-1706885027-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-5-1706885027-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-5-1706885027-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-340723%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAryan%20won%20the%20Pradhan%20Mantri%20Rashtriya%20Bal%20Puraskar%20for%20his%20innovation.%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20robot%20is%20fully%20run%20on%20solar%20energy.%20%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20a%20piezoelectric%20panel%20installed%20in%20it%20that%20uses%20pressure%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F331384%2Fkota-engineer-runs-sustainable-dairy-farm-saves-electricity-bills-biogas-plant-video%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproduce%20electricity.%20%3C%2Fa%3EFor%20instance%2C%20the%20pressure%20created%20on%20the%20tyres%20and%20the%20panel%20will%20produce%20electricity%20that%20can%20be%20stored%20in%20the%20batteries%20for%20use%20when%20the%20sun%20is%20down%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSo%20this%20creates%20a%20chain%20of%20power%2C%20once%20the%20solar%20energy%20is%20exhausted%20you%20can%20switch%20to%20a%20piezoelectric%20panel.%20The%20robot%20will%20not%20need%20any%20external%20source%20whatsoever%20to%20work%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20robot%20has%20garnered%20a%20lot%20of%20attention%20and%20Aryan%20has%20already%20set%20up%20a%20company%20to%20commercialise%20the%20robot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20aim%20is%20to%20reach%20each%20and%20every%20hardworking%20%3Cem%3Ekisan%20%3C%2Fem%3Eof%20the%20country.%20I%20am%20planning%20to%20commercialise%20the%20robot%20to%20make%20it%20more%20accessible%20to%20the%20farmers.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecalling%20an%20incident%20at%20Krishi%20Mela%20in%20Kota%2C%20Aryan%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThere%20were%20a%20lot%20of%20innovators%20around%20me%20and%20I%20was%20very%20nervous.%20But%20the%20robot%20garnered%20so%20much%20attention%20that%20hundreds%20of%20people%2C%20mostly%20farmers%2C%20visited%20my%20stall%20and%20showed%20interest%20in%20my%20work.%20Narendra%20Singh%20Tomar%2C%20who%20is%20an%20MLA%20visited%20my%20stall%20and%20congratulated%20me%20on%20my%20innovation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20feels%20surreal%20but%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20I%20could%20bring%20such%20an%20innovation%20for%20the%20farmers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%3B%20All%20images%20courtesy%3A%20Aryan%20Singh)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706885858000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2Fleather-4-170688500