0in%20width%20and%20height%20produces%20a%20distinct%20echo%20compared%20to%20the%20entrance.%20Students%2C%20as%20part%20of%20their%20training%2C%20walk%2C%20talk%2C%20and%20even%20clap%20to%20practise%20using%20different%20techniques%20for%20identifying%20spaces%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESight%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20navigation%20easy%20for%20students%20who%20can%20perceive%20colour%20in%20light%2C%20he%20used%20different%20colours.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGiven%20that%20many%20low%20vision%20students%20are%20studying%20in%20the%20school%2C%20another%20aspect%20we%20had%20to%20consider%20was%20using%20contrasting%20colours%20and%20lighting%20to%20help%20students%20identify%20objects%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F320628%2Fheta-pandit-writes-stories-from-goan-homes-book-on-culture-family-food%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efurniture%2C%20and%20spaces%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20each%20classroom%20door%20is%20brightly%20painted%2C%20the%20entrance%20is%20in%20a%20different%20bright%20colour%2C%20and%20the%20toilet%20doors%20are%20painted%20in%20contrasting%20yet%20vibrant%20colours.%20This%20approach%20ensures%20that%20students%20with%20low%20vision%20can%20readily%20identify%20and%20locate%20important%20elements%2C%20such%20as%20the%20switchboard.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESmell%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20to%20make%20the%20classrooms%20even%20more%20distinctive%20from%20each%20other%2C%20the%20architect%20decided%20to%20engage%20the%20sense%20of%20smell.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20also%20planted%20aromatic%20plants%20at%20entries%2C%20which%20can%20assist%20students%20in%20marking%20and%20identifying%20places.%20These%20elements%20serve%20as%20different%20clues%20inco